snippet.title: Gran Turismo Sport - SPEC II Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/gran-turismo-sport/?emcid=or-1s-412983

Almost 2 years after the launch of GT Sport, an updated “SPEC II” version will be available at select retailers and the PlayStation Store (internet connection required) starting from today, October 4th. The new version will contain the base game plus all the free content updates up until May. This means you will find over 280 cars included and over 25 tracks!

https://www.gran-turismo.com/us/
